'DOS PRODOS CATALOG 2'; SIMILAR TOTHE 'DOS PRODOS CATALOG' ONE-LINERFROM NIBBLE VOL. 7/NO. 6 (JUNE1986); WILL EXECUTE THE APPROPRIATE'CATALOG' OR 'CAT' COMMAND DEPENDINGON WHETHER ITIS RUN UNDER DOS 3.3 OR PRODOS. THISVERSION; HOWEVER; ALSO DETECTSWHETHER YOU'RE IN 40-COLUMN OR80-COLUMN MODE AND; UNDER PRODOS;USES 'CAT' OR 'CATALOG'RESPECTIVELY.THIS ONE-LINER WAS ORIGINALLYPUBLISHED IN THE 'LETTERS' SECTIONOF NIBBLE VOL. 8/NO. 7 (JULY 1987).